directions: ["Sprinkle 1 teaspoon of salt over cabbage and let stand 1 hour. Squeeze out fluid.", "Mix cabbage, celery and green pepper."]

title: Lazy Man'S Stuffed Cabbage
ingredients: ["1 1/2 lb. ground beef", "1 small onion, chopped", "1 head cabbage, shredded or torn", "1 can tomato soup", "1 can water", "1 can tomato sauce", "1 can water", "1 c. Minute rice"]
directions: ["Put cabbage in boiling water; cook until slightly soft. Drain.", "Brown ground beef and onions until onions are clear and beef loses its pink.", "Drain.", "Add tomato soup, tomato sauce and water to meat.", "Prepare Minute rice as directed on package.", "Add meat and tomato mixture.", "In an 11 x 15-inch baking pan, layer cabbage and meat-tomato mixture; repeat once more.", "Cover with aluminum foil; bake in a 350\u00b0 oven for 1 hour."]
